CustomField.description: This field is optional and is manually populated. This field indicates whether or not the statistic should be calculated. A value of TRUE indicates that the statistic must be calculated. If the field is not specified, the field will be set to FALSE, which indicates that the statistic is not active and should not be calculated.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Boolean that controls if the configuration is active or not.
CustomField.label: Active
